"definition": "(航海) 帆を上げる、旗を掲げる",
"english_definition": "(nautical) to hoist, to raise (a sail or flag)",
"examples": [
{
"sentence": "Issare le vele.",
"translation": "帆を上げる。"
},
{
"sentence": "Issare la bandiera.",
"translation": "旗を掲げる。"
}
],
"collocations": [
